<para style="q1">

<verse number="49" style="v" />Lord, where are your former acts of covenant faithfulness</para>

<para style="q1">that you swore to David in your truthfulness?</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="50" style="v" />Call to mind, Lord, the mocking directed against your servants</para>

<para style="q1">and how I bear in my heart so many insults from the nations.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="51" style="v" />Your enemies hurl insults, Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">they mock the footsteps of your anointed one.</para>

